  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "For one thing, while convolutional methods for image fusion excel at extracting local features, they often struggle to capture broader global information.",
    "This shortfall can lead to output images with reduced clarity and increased noise.",
    "To address this challenge, several researchers have incorporated GANs into image fusion.",
    "(Tang et al. 2022) developed a multiscale adaptive transformer fusion approach to enhance the preservation of global contextual information when fusing MRI and single photon emission computed tomography images.",
    "(Rao et al. 2023) developed TGFuse employing a lightweight transformer component and adversarial learning to enhance the integration of shallow features, refining fusion relations both spatially and across channels."
  ],
